## Is it possible to add the same service account to multiple teams?

You can’t add a service account to multiple teams in W&B. Each service account is tied to a specific team.

## Is there a monthly subscription option for the Teams plan?

The Teams plan doesn’t offer a monthly subscription option. It’s billed annually.

